'''ZETH''' is a level editor designed exclusively for [[ZDoom]], based on {{dw|DETH}} (which was in turn based on {{dw|Doom_Editing_Utilities|DEU}}) by Jim Flynn. Currently runs in a DOS environment, but an unfinished Windows/Linux version is also available.

Development of WinZETH has completely ceased in 2004. [[Doom Builder|Doom Builder 2 or GZDoom Builder]] and [[SLADE|SLADE 3]] allow to use recent ZDoom and [[GZDoom]] editing features in Windows and Windows/Linux/OS X environments.

